{"tid":638862,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[死tb抵9死] 「手機先食」未及撳𨋢　短髮女遭醉漢擸電筒扑爆頭","createTime":"2018-04-23T05:32:16.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-23T05:52:49.000Z","uid":58335,"like":19,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"d9b4c36acf680310f7529c9b8308f9471bf8a636","tid":638862,"uid":58335,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-23T05:32:16.000Z","msg":"你老母，冇事就扮男人作威作福串串貢<br />\n有事就用女人身份屈人非禮<br />\n醉酒佬都去野<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n企係位唔㩒已經掛住影相on99<br />\n人地都係啤下你<br />\n你走去串串貢撩人？<br />\n肯定又想係條tbg面前扮有型<br />\n抵9死<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n葵涌女子掛住影相開心Share冇撳升降機掣，慘遭惡漢擸電筒扑爆頭要縫針！今晨零時27分，一名任職電訊公司26歲蓄短髮姓沈女子，與一名同齡女友人消遣後返回她葵涌邨的寓所，兩人於葵涌街市一間便利店購買兩支甜筒後，步入電梯大堂等候升降機，期間兩女「手機先食」專心拍攝甜筒，疑樂極忘形，未有撳升降機掣，隨後一名染有金髮及帶有酒意男子，疑不滿被耽誤時間怒睥兩女。 <br />\n<br />\n沈女見對方怒目而視出言稱：「你再睥住我就叫非禮！」雙方隨即發生爭執，沈女被人出手叉頸襲擊，由電梯大堂推打至商場，期間有兩名由升降機步出的男街坊見狀，上前試圖將兩人分開，金毛漢大叫：「佢x我老x我咪打佢老x臭x咯！仆x！」男街坊向沈女謂：「人哋咁大隻，佢飲醉酒，唔好追究，走啦，企喺度無意思」惟沈女指自己被打傷，報警求助，對方聞言更脫衣大嚷：「你嚇鬼呀！」其後離開現場，沈女與女友人則步往便利店外等候警員到場。 <br />\n<br />\n惟金毛漢3分鐘後折返，手持一支約一尺長電筒衝前向沈女右後腦狂扑，沈女閃避不及登時頭破血流，醉漢傷人後持電筒逃離現場，遇襲沈女後腦受傷流血，由接報到場救護員送院救治。警方於附近兜截，於案發現場附近葵涌邨碧葵樓一單位，發現涉嫌傷人姓譚(51歲)男子，將其拘捕帶署扣查。 <br />\n<br />\n沈女兄長接報趕抵醫院了解事件，他向記者稱，其妹遇襲右手臂及右背被扑至紅腫，而後腦被爆頭需縫兩針，他續指：「無諗過唔撳lift會畀人打！」 <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180423/mobile/bkn-20180423054009238-0423_00822_001.html#&amp;gid=1&amp;pid=2\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180423%2Fmobile%2Fbkn-20180423054009238-0423_00822_001.html%23%26gid%3D1%26pid%3D2&d=xIz6K2mQAbF9OPZ6klPFWDA5unq%2FSd9ZKvr75NUD1%2F0%3D&h=4e2357a1\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180423/mobile/bkn-20180423054009238-0423_00822_001.html#&amp;gid=1&amp;pid=2</a>"},{"pid":"fc2ef3711e5d862749778b6e4b2b51bf8150c07a","tid":638862,"uid":128600,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-23T05:38:43.000Z","msg":"係開心既"},{"pid":"2dbf3b18da0f2d57ee1803ee9cfb1b67ed88115f","tid":638862,"uid":17765,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-23T05:40:28.000Z","msg":"你再睥住我就叫非禮！<br />\n<br />\n冇波冇鳩更冇腦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fa5e12507140016c60693e10f0b803b302f95fe2","tid":638862,"uid":2419,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-23T05:40:31.000Z","msg":"死tb<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6779b0d6e40f0dab1d7ded2428edce5ea2daba28","tid":638862,"uid":123053,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-23T05:41:18.000Z","msg":"死tb狗低比人打<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"22f8273e1b110ff97d1401e1adca40ffaab011b2","tid":638862,"uid":29080,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-23T05:41:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2c508408251c94fa72b79367100ae9639b8c1812","tid":638862,"uid":44117,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-23T05:43:23.000Z","msg":"畀人爆頭後有冇影張打卡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a3d8afc12ca27793b0d2298bece0a77ccaf0e9c9","tid":638862,"uid":58335,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"2c508408251c94fa72b79367100ae9639b8c1812","tid":638862,"uid":44117,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-23T05:43:23.000Z","msg":"畀人爆頭後有冇影張打卡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-23T05:44:20.000Z","msg":"有都唔定<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n手機打卡第一<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d0d60f2b4df1efa85055d1509d52fece79f523ca","tid":638862,"uid":99205,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-23T05:47:47.000Z","msg":"扮到成個男人咁<br />\n<br />\n醉酒佬打過來又保護唔到自己<br />\n<br />\n都係扮翻女人啦"},{"pid":"4d36c7459516c62349b2a2da1b47b8a3dc389104","tid":638862,"uid":99205,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-23T05:52:49.000Z","msg":"屌<br />\n原來屈人非禮在先<br />\n然後又報警<br />\n<br />\n大佬做得TB當然當係男人<br />\n2個人對一個阿叔<br />\n俾人地拉扯下咪算<br />\n仲報警,抵俾人尋仇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}